# ── Map tile provider ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# The default tile URL is CARTO light_all (no key required for light traffic).
# To switch to MapTiler, Mapbox, or another provider, set VITE_TILE_URL.
# If you change providers, also update the TILE_ATTRIBUTION string in src/js/app.js
# to satisfy the new provider's terms of service.
#
# MapTiler example:
#   VITE_TILE_URL=https://api.maptiler.com/maps/streets/{z}/{x}/{y}.png?key=YOUR_KEY
#
# Mapbox example:
#   VITE_TILE_URL=https://api.mapbox.com/styles/v1/mapbox/light-v11/tiles/{z}/{x}/{y}?access_token=YOUR_TOKEN
#
VITE_TILE_URL=
